510
00:20:57,625 --> 00:20:59,291
Who do you think you are?

511
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:02,791
That cannot be! It's impossible!

512
00:21:02,875 --> 00:21:05,458
None of this is in the guide

513
00:21:05,541 --> 00:21:07,833
to my divine destiny
in the Gospel

514
00:21:07,916 --> 00:21:09,041
What are you?!

515
00:21:09,125 --> 00:21:11,500
Just what are you?!

516
00:21:11,583 --> 00:21:14,041
- You ask the same things
over and over.

517
00:21:14,125 --> 00:21:16,541
If you're having
nightmares,
then welcome to the club.

518
00:21:16,625 --> 00:21:17,916
- Then, then, then, then,
then, then, then...

519
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,125
you are truly Pride
in the flesh.

520
00:21:20,208 --> 00:21:23,000
- Wrong!
My name's Subaru Natsuki!

521
00:21:23,083 --> 00:21:27,416
And I am the knight of Emilia,
the silver-haired half-elf.

522
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,666
- [shrieking]

523
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,666
- I don't know anything
about this Pride stuff.

524
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:33,625
The only title I want
is Emilia's knight.

525
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:34,458
I don't need any others.

526
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:39,500
[Authority moaning]

527
00:21:39,583 --> 00:21:41,791
- What a strange-looking place.

528
00:21:41,875 --> 00:21:43,750
- Yes, it is.

529
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:45,708
It's a place
where my time once ended.

530
00:21:45,791 --> 00:21:47,291
But this go-around,

531
00:21:47,375 --> 00:21:49,750
it'll be the one
where your time ends instead,

532
00:21:49,833 --> 00:21:51,791
the last place you'll ever see.

533
00:21:54,833 --> 00:21:55,916
- If your goal
was to lead me out here,

534
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:58,833
what do you have
prepared for me?

535
00:21:58,916 --> 00:22:00,250
What futile plan
is up your sleeve?

536
00:22:00,333 --> 00:22:03,833
- It's a good one,
your natural enemy,

537
00:22:03,916 --> 00:22:05,875
one you and I
happen to have in common.

538
00:22:05,958 --> 00:22:06,916
- [gasps]

539
00:22:08,916 --> 00:22:09,958
- Your natural enemy, huh?

540
00:22:10,041 --> 00:22:12,875
Now, that's a fine thing
to call me.

541
00:22:12,958 --> 00:22:15,041
[spirits warbling]

542
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:22,125
- I'm one of the Lugunica
Imperial Knights,

543
00:22:22,208 --> 00:22:23,791
Julius Euclius.

544
00:22:23,875 --> 00:22:26,250
For my kingdom,
I must now slay you.

545
00:22:26,333 --> 00:22:30,416
- So you're a spirit arts user,
are you?

546
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:32,083
Well, h-how truly--

547
00:22:32,166 --> 00:22:33,000
h-how truly--

548
00:22:33,083 --> 00:22:36,166
Is this also part of your plot?

549
00:22:36,250 --> 00:22:39,541
I have never known such
humiliation in my entire life.

550
00:22:39,625 --> 00:22:40,291
- Oh, really?

551
00:22:40,375 --> 00:22:42,833
Well, you should
make the most of it.

552
00:22:42,916 --> 00:22:45,500
'Cause that's the bill for
all the trouble you've caused.

553
00:22:45,583 --> 00:22:46,916
- [grunts]

554
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,750
- Let's do it, Julius.

555
00:22:48,833 --> 00:22:50,208
- You sure about this?

556
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:51,875
- I won't back down.

557
00:22:51,958 --> 00:22:54,458
I won't bend. I can't fail,

558
00:22:54,541 --> 00:22:56,791
and I don't want
to lose anybody else.

559
00:22:56,875 --> 00:23:00,125
- I am the man who brutally beat
and humiliated you.

560
00:23:00,208 --> 00:23:03,000
Looking back on it,
I still believe my behavior

561
00:23:03,083 --> 00:23:05,458
was backed
by meaning and reason,

562
00:23:05,541 --> 00:23:07,958
but that is no more
than self-justification,

563
00:23:08,041 --> 00:23:10,000
which has
nothing to do with you.

564
00:23:11,875 --> 00:23:13,666
Are you able to trust me?

565
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:16,416
Will you put your faith in me?

566
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:19,625
- Listen. I still hate
your freakin' guts.

567
00:23:19,708 --> 00:23:21,958
- Yes, I'm well aware of that.

568
00:23:22,041 --> 00:23:23,708
- You broke my arms and legs.

569
00:23:23,791 --> 00:23:25,458
That's a pretty traumatic thing,
you know?

570
00:23:25,541 --> 00:23:27,125
Haven't you ever heard
the word "restraint"?

571
00:23:27,208 --> 00:23:29,625
- Just so you're aware,

572
00:23:29,708 --> 00:23:31,666
I did hold back
quite a bit that day.

573
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:34,958
- Seriously? That wasn't
everything you had?

574
00:23:35,041 --> 00:23:38,458
Man, you really are
the biggest jerk I've ever met.

575
00:23:38,541 --> 00:23:41,000
I truly hate you,
"Greatest of Knights,"

576
00:23:41,083 --> 00:23:42,708
and I always will.

577
00:23:43,916 --> 00:23:45,000
Even so...

578
00:23:45,083 --> 00:23:48,166
I'll put my trust in you.

579
00:23:48,250 --> 00:23:49,625
The shame I feel
that began that day,

580
00:23:49,708 --> 00:23:53,666
attests to my knowledge that you
are an incredible knight.

581
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:54,166
- I see.

582
00:23:54,250 --> 00:23:56,125
Then with all my soul,

583
00:23:56,208 --> 00:24:00,000
I will live up to that trust!

584
00:24:00,083 --> 00:24:00,791
[chorus vocalizing]

585
00:24:00,875 --> 00:24:03,666
- Is this ridiculous farce
over yet?!

586
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:05,541
What do you expect
to accomplish

587
00:24:05,625 --> 00:24:08,708
by adding a single
spirit arts user to your ranks?

588
00:24:08,791 --> 00:24:09,875
I will defeat you all,

589
00:24:09,958 --> 00:24:11,666
tear apart those who remain,

590
00:24:11,750 --> 00:24:14,083
resume the Ordeal,
and you can't stop me!

591
00:24:14,166 --> 00:24:17,166
My diligence knows not
of slothful resignation,

592
00:24:17,250 --> 00:24:18,708
nor of demise!

593
00:24:18,791 --> 00:24:21,625
[shrieking]

594
00:24:21,708 --> 00:24:25,041
Sloth! Sloth!
Sloth! Sloth! Sloth!

595
00:24:25,125 --> 00:24:28,041
- Now,<i> Al Clarista!</i>

596
00:24:29,208 --> 00:24:30,833
- [chuckling]

597
00:24:30,916 --> 00:24:32,583
[gasps]

598
00:24:37,916 --> 00:24:38,541
No way.

599
00:24:38,625 --> 00:24:40,833
You should
not be able to see it.

600
00:24:40,916 --> 00:24:42,958
It should be invisible to you.

601
00:24:43,041 --> 00:24:45,791
My Unseen Hand
can't be--can't be seen!

602
00:24:45,875 --> 00:24:47,000
You can't see it!

603
00:24:47,083 --> 00:24:49,291
Yet two people did
other than me.

604
00:24:49,375 --> 00:24:52,666
- I'm the only one
who can see it, Betelgeuse.

605
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:54,041
- Huh?!

606
00:24:54,125 --> 00:24:56,125
- Julius can only see
what I'm seeing.

607
00:24:56,208 --> 00:24:58,083
Right now,
we're both sharing my vision,

608
00:24:58,166 --> 00:25:01,083
although it's a much creepier
feeling than I thought it'd
be.

609
00:25:01,166 --> 00:25:03,333
- I can use<i> Nect</i> to consciously
share some of your senses,

610
00:25:03,416 --> 00:25:07,416
as well as to maintain them
for a while.

611
00:25:07,500 --> 00:25:09,958
I must admit, when you
first proposed this plan to me,

612
00:25:10,041 --> 00:25:12,541
I questioned your sanity.

613
00:25:12,625 --> 00:25:13,750
- Well, it worked,
though, didn't it?

614
00:25:13,833 --> 00:25:17,666
Gotta have guts sometimes
and be willing to try anything.

615
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:19,041
- [chuckles]

616
00:25:19,125 --> 00:25:19,916
- Curse you!

617
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,208
Curse you! Curse you!

618
00:25:22,291 --> 00:25:24,833
Curse you! Curse you!
Curse you!

619
00:25:24,916 --> 00:25:28,000
Curse you! Bah!

620
00:25:28,083 --> 00:25:28,750
- [gasps]

621
00:25:28,833 --> 00:25:30,875
Sharing a collective body
with you

622
00:25:30,958 --> 00:25:32,875
is a pretty disgusting
experience.

623
00:25:32,958 --> 00:25:34,750
Let's get this over with,
already!

624
00:25:34,833 --> 00:25:35,666
- Yes, shall we?

625
00:25:39,291 --> 00:25:39,666
- [chuckles]

626
00:25:41,666 --> 00:25:44,041
