a bit of concern.

631
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:04,958
I would like to take

632
00:26:05,041 --> 00:26:06,916
a small number of our forces
to eliminate it.

633
00:26:08,125 --> 00:26:09,125
- [sighs]

634
00:26:09,208 --> 00:26:10,125
What about me?

635
00:26:10,208 --> 00:26:11,791
Could I not be of any help?

636
00:26:14,166 --> 00:26:16,291
- No, Miss Emilia.

637
00:26:16,375 --> 00:26:18,166
Please head to safety
in the carriage,

638
00:26:18,250 --> 00:26:20,875
and hold on to these children's
hands tightly, all right?

639
00:26:20,958 --> 00:26:23,416
- [sighs]

640
00:26:24,708 --> 00:26:26,208
- The two of you
are truly master and servant.

641
00:26:26,291 --> 00:26:29,166
I can see the same thing
in your eyes

642
00:26:29,250 --> 00:26:30,708
that I see in his.

643
00:26:31,916 --> 00:26:32,875
- Uh...

644
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:38,333
Thank you, Wilhelm.

645
00:26:38,416 --> 00:26:39,958
You've done--[gasps]

646
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:43,416
[sighs]

647
00:26:48,833 --> 00:26:49,750
- [Julius yelling]
- [chorus vocalizing]

648
00:27:06,208 --> 00:27:07,875
- No! Impossible!

649
00:27:07,958 --> 00:27:09,125
This cannot be!

650
00:27:09,208 --> 00:27:12,125
You cannot use such means,
such evil tricks

651
00:27:12,208 --> 00:27:14,875
to make light of me
and my undying devotion!

652
00:27:14,958 --> 00:27:16,166
[wails]

653
00:27:20,458 --> 00:27:21,416
- [winces]

654
00:27:21,958 --> 00:27:23,875
[groans]

655
00:27:23,958 --> 00:27:24,416
- [groans]

656
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,375
This is some crappy game

657
00:27:26,458 --> 00:27:28,041
where, as soon
as you're caught, it's over.

658
00:27:28,125 --> 00:27:31,333
We must be out of our minds to
entrust our lives to those
odds,

659
00:27:31,416 --> 00:27:32,416
completely insane.

660
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:34,916
- My body's slowly
getting used to this.

661
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,875
Shall we speed up?

662
00:27:36,958 --> 00:27:38,625
- Sounds good.
Don't worry about me!

663
00:27:45,583 --> 00:27:47,375
