664
00:27:47,458 --> 00:27:48,916
- Impossible!

665
00:27:49,041 --> 00:27:50,041
Impossible! Impossible!

666
00:27:50,125 --> 00:27:53,083
Impossible! Impossible!
Impossible!

667
00:27:53,166 --> 00:27:55,125
How can it be?

668
00:27:55,208 --> 00:27:56,791
Why is this happening?!

669
00:27:56,875 --> 00:27:58,333
I thought I was loved, loved!

670
00:27:58,416 --> 00:28:00,416
I am loved, loved by her,

671
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:03,000
by the Witch! By the Witch!
By the Witch! By the Witch!

672
00:28:03,083 --> 00:28:04,791
By the Witch!

673
00:28:04,875 --> 00:28:08,166
- It's time I put an end to you
once and for all! [grunts]

674
00:28:08,250 --> 00:28:12,041
- [yelling]

675
00:28:15,166 --> 00:28:17,416
<i>Al Clauseria!</i>

676
00:28:21,875 --> 00:28:24,041
- [gasping]

677
00:28:30,291 --> 00:28:33,000
I won't let you do that.

678
00:28:33,083 --> 00:28:34,041
<i>Ul Dona!</i>

679
00:28:38,291 --> 00:28:39,000
- Burn, fighting spirit!

680
00:28:39,083 --> 00:28:41,208
Howl, magic ball!

681
00:28:41,291 --> 00:28:43,541
I get serious,
I can pitch like a pro!

682
00:28:45,250 --> 00:28:45,875
- What is this?

683
00:28:49,541 --> 00:28:50,500
[sword stabs]

684
00:28:51,583 --> 00:28:52,458
[gagging]

685
00:28:52,541 --> 00:28:54,291
- Your mistake cost you.

686
00:28:54,375 --> 00:28:56,458
You considered your enemy
weak and powerless.

687
00:28:56,541 --> 00:28:58,916
My blade, all six elements,

688
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,250
will slice your very soul apart,

689
00:29:01,333 --> 00:29:02,958
scattered to the end
of the rainbow.

690
00:29:03,041 --> 00:29:04,416
- No, I refuse to let it end.

691
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:06,125
This faithful servant
has been nothing

692
00:29:06,208 --> 00:29:07,708
but diligent in his duties.

693
00:29:07,791 --> 00:29:10,750
The love of the Witch,
it bathes my entire body!

694
00:29:10,833 --> 00:29:13,333
- [gasps] Julius, we need
to undo<i> Nect</i> right now!

695
00:29:13,416 --> 00:29:15,500
- As you wish, then.

696
00:29:18,375 --> 00:29:21,125
- [laughs] My brain...

697
00:29:21,208 --> 00:29:23,041
it trembles!

698
00:29:23,125 --> 00:29:25,750
SUBARU: Yeah, just tremble
while you wait inside me.

699
00:29:25,833 --> 00:29:28,416
I'll let you meet her
just this one time, okay?

700
00:29:28,500 --> 00:29:30,125
BETELGEUSE:
What's that? Meet whom?

701
00:29:30,208 --> 00:29:31,833
Now what are you
talking about, boy?

702
00:29:31,916 --> 00:29:33,375
SUBARU: The Witch
you've been waiting to see

703
00:29:33,458 --> 00:29:35,208
face to face your entire life!

704
00:29:35,291 --> 00:29:37,458
[inhales]

705
00:29:37,541 --> 00:29:40,166
I can use Return by Death to...

706
00:29:44,541 --> 00:29:45,958
- Hmm?

707
00:29:46,041 --> 00:29:47,750
[gasps]

708
00:29:50,125 --> 00:29:52,958
[squeals]

709
00:29:53,041 --> 00:29:53,458
Ah, yes.

710
00:29:53,541 --> 00:29:56,958
I've waited so long,

711
00:29:57,041 --> 00:29:58,541
waited for your love,

712
00:29:58,625 --> 00:30:01,000
merciful love,
affectionate love,

713
00:30:01,083 --> 00:30:03,291
[gasps]

714
00:30:06,250 --> 00:30:07,500
[gasping]

715
00:30:07,583 --> 00:30:08,875
- No.

716
00:30:08,958 --> 00:30:10,250
You're not the one.

717
00:30:10,333 --> 00:30:12,000
- [squeals]

718
00:30:13,208 --> 00:30:14,166
- [chorus vocalizes]
- [gasps]

719
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:16,208
I made it back. [groans]

720
00:30:16,291 --> 00:30:17,875
- This cannot--

721
00:30:17,958 --> 00:30:20,333
No, it--it cannot be.

722
00:30:20,416 --> 00:30:22,958
- I was prepared to keep
doing that over and over again

723
00:30:23,041 --> 00:30:24,041
until you finally left me,

724
00:30:24,125 --> 00:30:26,375
but you gave up
after just one go at it?

725
00:30:26,458 --> 00:30:28,250
How big of a coward
are you, freak?

726
00:30:28,333 --> 00:30:31,166
- Take your last breath.
I'm ending you.

727
00:30:31,250 --> 00:30:32,500
- [gurgles]

728
00:30:32,583 --> 00:30:34,541
[groans]

729
00:30:34,625 --> 00:30:35,083
But why?

730
00:30:35,166 --> 00:30:37,625
Why? Tell me.

731
00:30:37,708 --> 00:30:39,375
Tell me why.

732
00:30:39,458 --> 00:30:41,083
After everything
I've done for you,

733
00:30:41,166 --> 00:30:44,291
I can't believe you'd abandon
your faithful servant like
this!

734
00:30:44,375 --> 00:30:50,291
Help me, Witch! Help me!

735
00:30:54,375 --> 00:30:56,708
Give your servant
the love he deserves.

736
00:31:01,333 --> 00:31:02,541
[Subaru sighs]

737
00:31:02,625 --> 00:31:05,000
Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti...

738
00:31:07,041 --> 00:31:08,416
you were Sloth.

739
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,041
No doubt about it.

740
00:31:18,666 --> 00:31:20,541
- Subaru, let's hurry back
to the village.

741
00:31:20,625 --> 00:31:22,500
- Hmm?
- Felix contacted me.

742
00:31:22,583 --> 00:31:26,125
It seems they have a problem.

743
00:31:26,208 --> 00:31:28,083
[music playing]

744
00:31:29,375 --> 00:31:32,541
- The magic stones of fire that
were in the merchants' inventory

745
00:31:32,625 --> 00:31:33,583
are nowhere to be found.

746
00:31:33,666 --> 00:31:36,166
OTTO: We unloaded
all of our cargo

747
00:31:36,250 --> 00:31:38,625
so we could take the villagers
on board more easily.

748
00:31:38,708 --> 00:31:40,375
Once we did, we noticed
that the stones were missing.

749
00:31:40,458 --> 00:31:43,000
- And what does that mean?

750
00:31:43,083 --> 00:31:45,250
- Most likely,
it means somebody

751
00:31:45,333 --> 00:31:47,458
left them on board when they
loaded the villagers.

752
00:31:47,541 --> 00:31:49,250
- They were last seen
in Ketty's carriage,

753
00:31:49,333 --> 00:31:51,083
and there are
enough magic stones

754
00:31:51,166 --> 00:31:54,333
packed away in there to easily
blow away a small village.

755
00:31:54,416 --> 00:31:56,000
- [no audible dialogue]

756
00:31:57,541 --> 00:32:00,208
And here's the worst of it.

757
00:32:00,291 --> 00:32:01,375
Ketty's carriage is the one

758
00:32:01,458 --> 00:32:03,750
taking Miss Emilia
and the children to the capital.

759
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:10,333
[no audible dialogue]

760
00:32:10,416 --> 00:32:11,666
- Miss Emilia.
- [gasps]

761
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:14,333
- It's time to get moving now.

762
00:32:14,416 --> 00:32:15,291
- [sighs]

